subject: Merge openpower_read_vpd and ibm_read_vpd.
commitMessage:
Merge openpower_read_vpd and ibm_read_vpd.

This commit merges the implementation of openpower_read_vpd_exe
and ibm_read_vpd exe.
Main objective is to have single exe irrespective of the type of
parser required.

Major modification includes:
1)Only one exe will be generated i.e ibm_read_vpd.
1)Modification in the code to populate dbus in case of openpower.
3)Get rid of auto generated header files.
4)Removal of app.cpp to have a single main when having a single
exe.
5)Removal of write.cpp,write.hpp, args.hpp, args.cpp.

This change require witherspoon system to work with json file for
inventory instead of yaml.
Json change commit for witherspoon:
https://gerrit.openbmc-project.xyz/c/openbmc/openpower-vpd-parser
/+/33457

Following command will build ibm_read_vpd exe for openpower-parser.
meson <directory>
ninja -C <directory>

Following command will build ibm_read_vpd exe for ibm-parser.
meson -Dibm-parser=enabled <directory>
ninja -C <directory>

Status:
Compilation ok.
Tested on Simics.
